<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>Email</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
    style="max-width: 600px; margin-top: 20px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px #ccc; border: none; border-radius: 5px;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px;">
            <img src="cid:logo.png" alt="Logo" style="display: block;" /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#ffffff"
            style="padding: 20px 0 10px; text-align: center; color: #555555; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;">
            <h3 style="margin: 15px 0; font-size: 23px;">Olá ${name},</h3>
            <p style="padding: 0 40px 20px; line-height: 1.5;">
                Você solicitou a alteração de senha no VIRTUS Way.<br />
                <br />Para completar a alteração, clique no link abaixo:
            </p> <a href="${url}"
            style="background: #132565; padding: 13px 23px; font-size: 16px; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; border: none; text-decoration: none;">Alterar
            senha </a>
            <p
            style="color: #999999; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 20px 0 0; margin-top: 40px;">Se
            você não reconhece este pedido de mudança de senha, ignore este e-mail.</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
